        27
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Palatine%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "The village’s name honors the Palatinate Germans who settled here in the mid‑1700s after fleeing French raids.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        14,
        16,
        17,
        18
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Palatine%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "The Frey House, Palatine Bridge Freight House, and Webster Wagner House are all listed on the National Register of Historic Places.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        5,
