      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia",
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Palatine%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "The Van Wie Farmstead, a historic farm, was added to the National Register in 2011.",
